@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ohnrcy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.15 + wp.abs((v0 + 0.07 + v0 + 0.67)))
    tmp = ((0.94 * wp.cos(v1 + 0.79)) + wp.exp(0.93))
    tmp = 0.67
    v1 = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = 0.60
    v0 = wp.exp((0.12 / wp.sin(v0 + 0.70)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.70) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.25)) / ((v2 + 0.56 - tmp + 0.82) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.52)))
    data[tid] = v0
